BT /F1 20 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 742 Tm (Design System Stable v1 Launch Checklist) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 716 Tm (Reusable checklist for deciding whether a design system is ready for a stable v1 launch.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 690 Tm (1. Freeze public API) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 670 Tm (- Finalize component names, prop names, defaults, and exports.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 654 Tm (- Remove or deprecate aliases before launch.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 638 Tm (2. Stabilize design tokens) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 618 Tm (- Freeze semantic token names and document token usage rules.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 602 Tm (- Eliminate ambiguous token paths.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 586 Tm (3. Complete component documentation) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 566 Tm (- Every component needs purpose, usage guidance, props, accessibility notes, examples, and composition guidance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 550 Tm (- Remove stale docs and outdated examples.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 534 Tm (4. Complete machine-readable contracts) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 514 Tm (- Keep manifests, discovery, schemas, examples, templates, prompts, and provider overlays current.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 498 Tm (- Keep package, runtime, manifest, and example versions aligned.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 482 Tm (5. Lock composition rules) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 462 Tm (- Define allowed parent/child relationships and enforce them in validation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 446 Tm (- Prevent ad hoc layout patterns where primitives already exist.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 430 Tm (6. Fix remaining component API gaps) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 410 Tm (- Audit every component spec and move legacy specs to one consistent format.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 394 Tm (- Ensure generated component API is complete enough for AI and docs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 378 Tm (7. Accessibility readiness) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 358 Tm (- Verify keyboard interaction, focus states, labeling, and ARIA behavior.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 342 Tm (- Run automated checks and manual keyboard testing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 326 Tm (8. Routing and host integration stability) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 306 Tm (- Ensure navigation components do not depend on one specific host runtime.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 290 Tm (- Support controlled routing props where needed.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 274 Tm (- Verify behavior in product apps, demo pages, and AI-generated hosts like Figma Make.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 258 Tm (9. Performance readiness) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 238 Tm (- Audit bundle size, CSS size, and demo-page or inspector performance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 222 Tm (- Remove expensive patterns or eager rendering where possible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 206 Tm (10. Testing baseline) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 186 Tm (- Typecheck, unit tests, integration tests, and AI governance checks must pass.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 170 Tm (- Add regression tests for recent bug fixes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 154 Tm (11. Visual regression coverage) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 134 Tm (- Snapshot or screenshot core components, states, responsive layouts, and brand/theme differences.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 118 Tm (12. Package publish hygiene) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 98 Tm (- Validate exports, CSS entrypoints, and npm pack contents.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 82 Tm (- Ensure tests, stories, and internal-only docs do not ship unless intentional.) Tj ET
endstream
