BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 742 Tm (13. Consumer install verification) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 722 Tm (- Test in a clean Vite app and a React Router app.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 706 Tm (- Verify styles import cleanly and app shell, menu, and scaffolds work from package install.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 690 Tm (14. AI readiness for launch) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 670 Tm (- Ensure layout recipes, Figma Make contract, provider overlays, and deterministic examples are current.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 654 Tm (15. Migration and deprecation policy) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 634 Tm (- Write migration notes, mark deprecated APIs clearly, and define support timelines.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 618 Tm (16. Release operations) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 598 Tm (- Create a release checklist, changelog, rollback procedure, and post-release triage path.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 582 Tm (17. Governance) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 562 Tm (- Decide who approves API changes after v1 and separate stable vs experimental components.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 536 Tm (Launch gate: do not call it v1 until API is frozen, docs and contracts are current, package installs cleanly, accessibility baseline is met, performance is acceptable, tests and validation are green, and consumers can build with it predictably.) Tj ET
endstream
